node.text: This is amazing! And looks yum

❤❤ Fruit Pastries.... another frozen prata hack.  Get your fruit pastries ready in 15 minutes. ⁣
⁣
I have tried using frozen prata for savory pies and egg tarts, as they are really versatile. Been thinking of fruit tarts but really lazy to make the crust from scratch, so thought of this fast and simple idea. Very happy with the end product 😍
⁣
⁣ 
For those interested to try out....
Ingredients ⁣
Frozen prata ⁣
Assorted fruits ⁣
Jam⁣
Icing sugar ⁣
⁣
Methods⁣
⭕ Use 2 sizes heart shape cookies cutter , cut out 2 big hearts, 1 for the base. Use the smaller cutter to cut the centre to make the top ring. ⁣
⭕ Poke some holes on the base to avoid it from puffing too much, and arrange the top ring.⁣
⭕ Airfried heart shape prata for about 10mins, 200deg in @mayerspore airfryer. ⁣
⭕ Remove from airfryer and cool.⁣
⭕ To assemble, put some jam on the base, put on your favourite fruits, sift some icing sugar on top.⁣
⭕ ❤❤ fruit pastries ready to serve !!!⁣
⁣
⁣Yummy!!!
